{
  "stem": "15962.6",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, we were primarily thinking of getting home and hoping, mostly, that somebody from our family survived and that we will meet with them.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I had still great hope that my mother will meet me when I get home.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I was no, in no shape to walk until-- [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] [SIGHS] let's say it was the first half of June [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] when I learned that a transport is-- transportation is being arranged for those who wanted to go to Czechoslovakia.",
      "word_count": 46
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There were isolated cases where the boys simply-- either two or three would just take off and try and fend for themselves and try and get home somehow.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they succeeded.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But those like myself who was not up to the task waited.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And in fact, I ran away from the hospital when I learned that this opportunity arose.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I joined the remaining boys.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And we were driven to a town called Linz that was [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] somewhat north of Horsching.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Because I don't think that the hospital would have released me.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Right.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I'll come to it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In Linz, which is on the Danube, the trucks took us to the harbor and put us on boats, but let's say one boat that I was in.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The Danube always had busy boat river traffic.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And there were probably very few boats left.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Anyway, the American-- there was one or two American soldiers who escorted us on this boat.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we arrived.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We were going east now on the Danube.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And suddenly we were-- we arrived in Melk, which is a town where we have been interned for two months.",
      "word_count": 20
    }
  ],
